26
00:00:48,582 --> 00:00:50,281
- They simply... Right.
- I see.

27
00:00:50,282 --> 00:00:52,151
They came to me and offered me an investment,

28
00:00:52,152 --> 00:00:54,221
- That's a good thing.
- but I simply thought...

29
