125
00:04:03,382 --> 00:04:05,081
Exactly. You should've asked her out instead of drawing a line with her.

126
00:04:05,082 --> 00:04:06,211
- I was worried...
- That was good, Ho Dong.

127
00:04:06,212 --> 00:04:07,981
