But he seems cautious about this.

135
00:04:22,232 --> 00:04:23,901
- He seems a bit...
- He must be interested in her.

136
00:04:23,902 --> 00:04:26,331
Knowing Jang Hoon's personality, drawing a line with her means...

137
00:04:26,332 --> 00:04:28,071
