- Absolutely.

138
00:04:28,072 --> 00:04:30,901
No, Hee Jin doesn't like a man like Jang Hoon.

139
00:04:30,902 --> 00:04:32,171
Don't you like a man like me?

140
00:04:32,172 --> 00:04:33,841
