- He has no prejudice.

158
00:05:06,312 --> 00:05:07,641
He's the one who should know when to stop.

159
00:05:07,642 --> 00:05:08,871
- But it's possible.
- Right, it's possible.

160
00:05:08,872 --> 00:05:10,281
- I mean, it's possible.
- There's no edge on the blades.

161
00:05:10,282 --> 00:05:11,381
Right. It's possible.

162
00:05:11,382 --> 00:05:12,581
There's no edge whatsoever.

163
00:05:12,582 --> 00:05:14,551
- He's Two Swords with no "swords."
- There's no edge whatsoever.

164
00:05:14,552 --> 00:05:15,611
- I have no marriage experience.
- I thought she had divorced before.

165
00:05:15,612 --> 00:05:16,921
- He has no prejudice.
- She has no marriage experience.

166
00:05:16,922 --> 00:05:19,621
Listen, everyone. Yeong Cheol's feelings were hurt.

167
00:05:19,622 --> 00:05:20,851
Yeong Cheol was the one who tried to impress her...

168
00:05:20,852 --> 00:05:22,491
while Jang Hoon kept playing hard to get.

169
00:05:22,492 --> 00:05:24,161
But she said Jang Hoon was attractive, so...

170
00:05:24,162 --> 00:05:26,532
Yeong Cheol kept telling me to ask her how she thought of him.

171
00:05:26,892 --> 00:05:29,562
