194
00:06:14,312 --> 00:06:16,682
- Oh, that's right.
- Hey, your uncle is unbelievable.

195
00:06:17,042 --> 00:06:18,341
- I'm right, am I not?
- No.

196
00:06:18,342 --> 00:06:20,081
I went to Canada in October.

197
00:06:20,082 --> 00:06:21,881
And I met my wife in January in the next year.

198
00:06:21,882 --> 00:06:23,721
- Oh, really? That confirms it.
- That's right.

199
00:06:23,722 --> 00:06:25,081
