- That was close.

200
00:06:25,082 --> 00:06:26,091
- That was close.
- No.

201
00:06:26,092 --> 00:06:27,191
"That was close?"

202
00:06:27,192 --> 00:06:29,091
- Only a few months after that...
- The time when he met his wife...

203
00:06:29,092 --> 00:06:31,091
