206
00:06:36,932 --> 00:06:37,962
When did I say that?

207
00:06:38,262 --> 00:06:39,901
Hold on. What if she said she liked you?

208
00:06:39,902 --> 00:06:41,531
- It's pointless...
- Hey, look at him.

209
00:06:41,532 --> 00:06:42,571
- Will you be okay?
- Don't be like that.

210
00:06:42,572 --> 00:06:43,701
- Your wife must be watching.
- You're being thoughtless.

211
00:06:43,702 --> 00:06:45,841
- What should he do now?
- Guys, this is...

212
00:06:45,842 --> 00:06:48,371
