- What if...

213
00:06:48,372 --> 00:06:50,341
- Sang Min and I...
- That was absurd.

214
00:06:50,342 --> 00:06:51,881
- co-hosted a TV show.
- Yes, we did.

215
00:06:51,882 --> 00:06:54,011
And we co-starred on "Invitation from Bachelor-agains."

216
00:06:54,012 --> 00:06:56,082
