- He would go home right away.

219
00:07:00,752 --> 00:07:02,622
So do you like having a chat personally?

220
00:07:03,762 --> 00:07:04,762
- Me?
- Yes.

221
00:07:04,763 --> 00:07:06,361
- "Me?"
- She was flustered.

222
00:07:06,362 --> 00:07:08,631
- He was waiting for a chance.
- That was so unexpected.

223
00:07:08,632 --> 00:07:09,831
- "Me?"
- What I mean is...

224
00:07:09,832 --> 00:07:11,961
