- Tell me something.

1010
00:34:00,719 --> 00:34:02,188
- I'm always sleepy.
- On a homeshopping channel.

1011
00:34:02,189 --> 00:34:03,858
- For people who are tired like her, - I recommend albumin.

1012
00:34:03,859 --> 00:34:05,558
they should take albumin.

1013
00:34:05,559 --> 00:34:07,988
When you feel dozy and tired,

1014
00:34:07,989 --> 00:34:10,058
it means that you need active oxygen.

1015
00:34:10,059 --> 00:34:13,558
This helps deliver oxygen and nutrients in your body...

1016
00:34:13,559 --> 00:34:15,598
like a delivery man, and it's called albumin.

1017
00:34:15,599 --> 00:34:17,238
It's 39.99 dollars for a box today.

1018
00:34:17,239 --> 00:34:18,768
We're giving you a 50 percent discount today.

1019
00:34:18,769 --> 00:34:21,008
- Me. Let me get them.
- We'll get you everything you need.

1020
00:34:21,009 --> 00:34:22,108
- Do you memorize them?
- So...

1021
00:34:22,109 --> 00:34:23,978
This is what I do for work, so it should come out right away.

1022
00:34:23,979 --> 00:34:26,179
By the way, Ho Dong's cushion...

1023
00:34:26,379 --> 00:34:28,578
- That was...
- I sold them too. Right.

1024
00:34:28,579 --> 00:34:29,908
Ho Dong was the model for that cushion.

1025
00:34:29,909 --> 00:34:31,678
I was the model for that before him.

1026
00:34:31,679 --> 00:34:33,148
- He took it after me.
- After you... That's right.

1027
00:34:33,149 --> 00:34:34,218
I did it first.

1028
00:34:34,219 --> 00:34:35,948
Jang Hoon was the model in the first season,

1029
00:34:35,949 --> 00:34:37,858
- For season 2.
- Ho Dong did it in the 2nd season.

1030
00:34:37,859 --> 00:34:40,559
Then which one did better? Season 1 or Season 2?

1031
00:34:40,829 --> 00:34:42,029
It was...

1032
00:34:42,989 --> 00:34:46,559
(Who's the top model in the cushions?)

1033
00:34:47,129 --> 00:34:48,499
- Well...
- Season Two did better.

1034
00:34:49,599 --> 00:34:51,638
(The home shopping emperor chose Ho Dong as the best model.)

1035
00:34:51,639 --> 00:34:53,768
- We did better in the Season Two.
- Look at him.

1036
00:34:53,769 --> 00:34:55,869
- All right.
- Next.

1037
00:34:56,139 --> 00:34:57,408
Now, we'll talk about...

1038
00:34:57,409 --> 00:34:59,438
the remarks of the four friends here.

1039
00:34:59,439 --> 00:35:01,278
- First, Jun Gyu wrote this.
- I wonder what it is.

1040
00:35:01,279 --> 00:35:03,378
