1041
00:35:03,379 --> 00:35:05,378
That's a given. Even when he was here the last time...

1042
00:35:05,379 --> 00:35:06,478
- We talked about it.
- Two Swords is...

1043
00:35:06,479 --> 00:35:08,088
It would be Two Swords even ten years later.

1044
