1047
00:35:14,129 --> 00:35:15,958
But that character goes so well with him.

1048
00:35:15,959 --> 00:35:18,129
That's not done just by his acting skills.

1049
00:35:18,599 --> 00:35:20,668
Your looks and everything.

1050
00:35:20,669 --> 00:35:22,068
They have to go well with it too, right?

1051
00:35:22,069 --> 00:35:24,238
- It can't be done just by effort.
- That's really important.

1052
00:35:24,239 --> 00:35:26,098
Even if someone wants to play the Two Swords...

1053
00:35:26,099 --> 00:35:28,568
I don't think it's a role that anyone can do it.

1054
00:35:28,569 --> 00:35:30,068
You have your YouTube channel, right?

1055
00:35:30,069 --> 00:35:31,779
Me? Yes, sir. Oh, I do.

1056
00:35:32,279 --> 00:35:33,279
What was that?

1057
00:35:33,479 --> 00:35:34,908
When I talk about my YouTube,

1058
00:35:34,909 --> 00:35:36,509
I get polite like this.

1059
00:35:36,709 --> 00:35:38,618
At my company,

1060
00:35:38,619 --> 00:35:40,148
