1061
00:35:40,149 --> 00:35:42,718
While doing that, I called Jang Hoon once.

1062
00:35:42,719 --> 00:35:45,358
And he said, "Sure. I'll be there." Then he appeared on it once.

1063
00:35:45,359 --> 00:35:46,718
- Jang Hoon visited him.
- So we did a shooting,

1064
00:35:46,719 --> 00:35:47,958
and it got a lot of views.

1065
