1067
00:35:53,899 --> 00:35:55,668
So I have felt bad about it since then.

1068
00:35:55,669 --> 00:35:56,928
- He's younger than me.
- Yes.

1069
00:35:56,929 --> 00:35:59,038
- I'll stop talking formally.
- Okay.

1070
00:35:59,039 --> 00:36:00,338
- Can I do that too?
- It got over a million views.

1071
00:36:00,339 --> 00:36:01,339
Quiet.

1072
00:36:01,569 --> 00:36:03,668
